  "playingCareerSummary": "Former Zimbabwe captain and wicket-keeper batter, widely regarded as Zimbabwe's greatest Test player: 63 Tests (4794 runs at 51.54), 213 ODIs (6786 runs). Did not play in the IPL. Brother of Grant Flower.",
